ne-block;">
<span>[9]</span>
</a>)</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Or another bank might have looked at those num=
bers, and the weirdness of the loans and the general bad environment right =
now, and said =E2=80=9Chmm, $197 billion of assets at a failed bank and I h=
ave a day to do due diligence, I=E2=80=99ll pay $150 billion for that.=E2=
=80=9D That=E2=80=99s enough to pay out the insured deposits and the FHLB, =
but it leaves only about 77=C2=A0cents on the dollar for the uninsured depo=
